e ceremony\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1324}, {\"ngram\": \"shelter\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1346}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a great idea.\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1368, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great idea\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1367}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The performances are awesome.\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1398, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The performances\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just wish it wasn't raining,\\\" said Pauline Brett, 69, who had come from Chicago with her family.\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1497, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1436, \"end\": 1443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_the_Apostle\", \"score\": 0.9947891333295277, \"rank\": 0.005234783570520376, \"text\": \"Pauline\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_the_Apostle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_the_Apostle\"}, {\"begin\": 1473, \"end\": 1480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"score\": 0.9999379297247672, \"rank\": 6.206093209991364e-05, \"text\": \"Chicago\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her family\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1496}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the City of Love, the ceremony stressed togetherness and unity in a world that has suffered wars, massacres, and political upheaval since the COVID-delayed Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1658, \"end\": 1672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999211459903895, \"rank\": 7.886022800460643e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phra